{"tid":1459332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈 機場活動 邊個衝就係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T04:20:09.000Z","uid":74083,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6451d2b529f80f5b8fcf1f73eb9890a3eaee85","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"利申 夢遊勇武派<br />\n由69 開始出黎<br />\n大大小小嘅戰役都有參與過<br />\n盾兵 消防 工兵 物資都做過<br />\n一直堅守兄弟爬山 3不原則<br />\n以為勇武先係取贏方法<br />\n<br />\n但經過呢2個月<br />\n義士 手足 同路人<br />\n傷嘅傷<br />\n被捕嘅被捕<br />\n仲有已經付出生命去喚醒其他人嘅烈士<br />\n香港人已經付出太多去對抗呢個不公嘅政府<br />\n<br />\n但我哋嘅訴求<br />\n一直都比人無視緊<br />\n<br />\n面對黑警嘅變招同變本加厲<br />\n勇武已經唔能夠完全對抗到<br />\n運動已經進入咗樽頸位<br />\n<br />\n難得一個和理非活動<br />\n同時又有實質重大嘅影響<br />\n一手揀住香港經濟命脈之一<br />\n威逼政府<br />\n<br />\n衝擊機場有咩實質作為？<br />\n邊個衝擊就係比籍口黑警再次清場<br />\n清咗場之後你估仲有無咁易比你入到去佔領？<br />\n<br />\n見到有人想衝擊<br />\n唔理係自己人定鬼<br />\n唔該捉停佢<br />\n今次機場唔係咁玩法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"b797d51604684cf9e812be345eb2b87d3b5eecbe","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b2b44af5b7895b2d66283ef530b20b70b5e916c","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"90aa6e85dd23c07881cb687499451517e5868b83","tid":1459332,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:45:18.000Z","msg":"有無人有&lsquo;&rsquo;琴日畀人拉咗嘅人&lsquo;&rsquo;嘅消息啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n24個鐘啦，見到律師未？佢地會唔會48個鐘之後都唔放人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eafd6d17b637695694012ad04e5f771907c04d","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:45:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b244abe3db34bbc91aa2f278334115ffc09329d5","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"adb7868c16da8cb7bbb0ef72dc3c68ba2ba6ee25","tid":1459332,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:59:01.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"de84fcba6f767b503f8e7f1fccc42215934118fc","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:00:27.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"cd20f2da7718cbc9c32e8476b2e4b9632832b6f3","tid":1459332,"uid":288231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:02:28.000Z","msg":"今日去機場只有2個情況<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死</span></span> OR <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有散水</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n我係我大台 ! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保持獨立思考"},{"pid":"58d7f0d01dfdfa0b92cbd6f85392f6ee77a886d6","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:04:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7d108839da6eb4ac8a4fc6a255a16fbb36ddfd46","tid":1459332,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:09:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c65e667bc5747e3cd1f7c10f2fd3cf9cbb0fdde","tid":1459332,"uid":290250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:10:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f747a7ef31f7b5aba946565c60289f4d077e12a5","tid":1459332,"uid":296222,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:13:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3bf0a5bea550ae19d8913c690f61d1c1b97742f","tid":1459332,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:13:36.000Z","msg":"見到有人衝全世界唔好跟住<br />\n極有可能係鬼<br />\n只係持續包圍機場已經可以令政府大量損失收益，日日去機場睇imax持續到一頭半個月政府實爆炸"},{"pid":"41e929374bb6aa1a03d22ea93dfb5816f8368e4d","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:06:38.000Z","msg":"嗰個 武裝起義 係咪勇武上腦定係黑警鬼<br />\n個個post 都話要衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次機場有咩衝？<br />\n衝又有咩意義？"},{"pid":"5982af0985531289ba9300989fa09b13f8d64fa2","tid":1459332,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"衝禁區等於送頭，邊個衝都唔會跟佢，就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"9f08f320e62eae3cd9a4a41265540d59c3ccb126","tid":1459332,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"樓主唔駛擔心<br />\n而家知道原來有香港警察入扮示威者<br />\n即係過往既衝都係佢地衝<br />\n乜衰野都係呢班香港警察做<br />\n燒差館燒返佢地自己友都做得出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而同一時間<br />\n示威者一直都係和平理性非暴力<br />\n暴力既係香港警察"},{"pid":"e89d8a43fbc2a8870067219f2bdaf8fcc3a66431","tid":1459332,"uid":200666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"a50e5fe6760dbec0bfde15cc9ee16d1d2cdf2981","tid":1459332,"uid":200666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1d66b770b12979e0075111c5f1507cff38bea9b","tid":1459332,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:35:57.000Z","msg":"NO衝擊"},{"pid":"f36ddacd16eb2cab0ccef9f07c5ea0864ed13d44","tid":1459332,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4328a17a0ffeec93ff6561c0d32c6b26f3d8d9","tid":1459332,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"有人衝禁區要制止, 機場你一個表達訴求嘅好地方,  要保住"},{"pid":"94ede2babe0abd7383ba2ecbe5f8f4d0ededf243","tid":1459332,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}